reviewText: Basic information but some of it quite helpful.  I wish my acupuncture school showed all or part of this video for our very first class.  It would've helped a lot.

graphic pictures are unclear; only spent less than 2 min exlaining 5 elements. explanation due to strong chinese accent is hard to understand.

first 10 min introduction pictures & speech are very unclear, hardly can hear what the expert was talking

very poor editing & quality !

it is not a quality product - buyer be aware!
